Oh. Thank you so much.

54:03.324 --> 54:04.407
You're welcome.

54:04.491 --> 54:06.659
Declan, meet her halfway, okay?

54:06.744 --> 54:07.994
You okay?

54:09.246 --> 54:10.330
Yeah.

54:11.624 --> 54:12.749
-Go ahead.
-LEAH: Thank you.

54:12.833 --> 54:14.417
All right.

54:14.501 --> 54:18.087
Coming down. Mr. Tilson, take it slow.

54:18.172 --> 54:19.964
