54:42.071 --> 54:43.738
Hi, Dale.

54:46.867 --> 54:50.453
Uh, there's more food if you're hungry.

54:52.122 --> 54:54.082
No, thanks, Mrs. Tilson.

54:55.376 --> 54:56.834
I really came to say goodbye.

54:58.754 --> 55:00.380
Where are you going?

55:02.383 --> 55:06.552
Listen. Uh... I understand how you feel.

55:08.639 --> 55:11.891
