to tell me to my face, though.

55:13.686 --> 55:14.978
(EXHALES DEEPLY)

55:15.062 --> 55:16.813
You're right.

55:18.941 --> 55:20.900
And I apologize.

55:23.904 --> 55:24.988
Well...

55:26.907 --> 55:29.283
It was a pleasure meeting you all.

55:31.245 --> 55:33.871
It was a pleasure meeting you, Dale.

55:40.546 --> 55:43.256
Great job integrating with the locals.

55:44.299 --> 55:46.592
It's for the best.

55:46.677 --> 55:49.262
(STAMMERING) The best for who, you?

55:50.848 --> 55:52.473
Um, maybe we should go feed Chester.

55:52.558 --> 55:53.766
